metadata.description:
HKO wanted to leave the narrow asteroid he lived on. And soon he fantasizes about running faster than a bird, gliding smoothly like a snake, and enjoying freedom. Suddenly, the Quantum Leap device starts to work, and HKO rides on a mysterious machine called "Roller Coaster" on Earth, which has never been seen before.


Oh no! After the first trip, HKO realized something was wrong with the device. HKO was originally a little black cat.
metadata.name: First Arrival - Rollercoaster #1/20
